### ============================================
### 基坑工程安全管理系统 - API 测试集合
### ============================================


### 临时接口：重置 admin 密码为 123456
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/reset-admin-pwd

### 1. 登录获取 Token（成功场景）
# @name login_success
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456"
}

> {%
    // 自动提取并保存 token
    client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.data.token);
    client.log("✅ 登录成功！");
    client.log("📝 Token: " + response.body.data.token.substring(0, 50) + "...");
    client.log("👤 用户: " + response.body.data.userInfo.username);
    client.log("🎭 角色: " + response.body.data.userInfo.roles.join(", "));
%}

###

### 2. 登录失败 - 错误密码
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

###

### 3. 登录失败 - 用户不存在
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "nonexistent",
  "password": "password"
}

###

### 4. 获取用户列表（需要认证）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/users
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 5. 获取特定用户信息
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 6. 无效 Token 测试
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/users
Authorization: Bearer invalid-token-12345
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 7. 无 Token 访问（应该被拒绝）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/users
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 8. 创建新用户（需要 ADMIN 权限）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/users
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "test123456",
  "realName": "测试用户",
  "phone": "13800138000",
  "roleIds": [2]
}

###

### 9. 修改用户信息
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/auth/users/2
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "realName": "修改后的名字",
  "phone": "13900139000",
  "status": 1,
  "roleIds": [2]
}

###

### 10. 删除用户
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/auth/users/2
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###
### 10. 删除用户
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/auth/users/2
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

