### ============================================
### 监测数据时序查询接口测试
### ============================================

### 11. 获取所有传感器编码列表
GET http://localhost:8081/api/monitor/sensors
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

###

### 12. 查询全站仪位移数据（FRHY-01）
GET http://localhost:8081/api/monitor/total-station?sensorCode=FRHY-01&startTime=2025-01-01 00:00:00&endTime=2025-12-31 23:59:59&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

###

### 13. 查询伺服轴力数据（SP1）
GET http://localhost:8081/api/monitor/axial-force?sensorCode=SP1&startTime=2025-01-01 00:00:00&endTime=2025-12-31 23:59:59&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

###

### 14. 查询钢支撑温度数据（6501945）
GET http://localhost:8081/api/monitor/steel-temperature?sensorCode=6501945&startTime=2025-01-01 00:00:00&endTime=2025-12-31 23:59:59&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

